dialogue.speaker: Agent
dialogue.text: Hello, Globex Inc, how can I help?

dialogue.speaker: Customer
dialogue.text: Hi, my name is Art Vandelay, account number GL-123. I can't seem to export my architectural drawings.

summary.introduction: Customer Art Vandelay called regarding an issue with exporting architectural drawings.
summary.solution: User was trying to export to a proprietary format. Advised to use standard PDF export from the File > Export menu.
summary.resolution: Resolved. The customer successfully exported their drawings to PDF.
